claimrbtokens().details: This function will be called by user, when he have atleast puchased 3 shoes.

confirmDeliveryOfShoeBySeller(uint256).details: The purpose of this function, to confirm from seller side that shoe has been deliverd. once this function is executed, the funds will be transfered to seller from escrow.

confirmDeliveryOfShoeByUser(uint256).details: The purpose of this function, to confirm from buyer side that shoe has been deliverd.

hasPurchasedShoe(address,uint256).details: IGNORE-- this function for now When User has two more than one shoe to choose.

linkAddressToSteps(string,address,uint25.details: IMP - WHEN USER PURCHASES A SHOE THIS FUNCTION WILL BE CALLED.

list(string,string,string,uint256,uint25.details: Function to list the shoe, seller/company can only list if they are KYC verified.

mapEmailToAddress(string,address).details: Function to map an email to an Ethereum address IMP - THIS FUNCTION WILL BE CALLED AFTER USER HITS THE CONNECT WALLET BUTTON-----//

mapEmailToSteps(string,uint256).details: Function to map an email to steps covered IMP - THIS FUNCTION WILL BE CALLED WHEN USER FETCHES HIS API DATA.

selectShoe(uint256).details: A user can have multiple shoes, through this function he/she will be able to decide which selecte shoe he/she want's to move on with. it will return the shoeId.

setUserHomeAddress(string).details: The purpose of this function, to set the Home Address for shipping purpose.
